2700:Just a moment ago, I hadn't been afraid to die. But the second I had lost control of my body, I had been overcome with a tremendous sense of dread.\p;
2800:<i>I</i> <i>d</i><i>o</i><i>n</i><i>'</i><i>t</i> <i>w</i><i>a</i><i>n</i><i>t</i> <i>t</i><i>o</i> <i>d</i><i>i</i><i>e</i><i>!</i>\p;
2900:Even if Yua-chan had died, I still wanted to live.\p;
3000:This was just my survival instincts taking over.\p;
3100:I screamed.\p;
3200:I screamed from the bottom of my soul.\p;
3300:I desperately reached out my hand to the distant night sky above me.\n;I knew there was no one that could grab onto it...\p;
3400:But I reached out all the same.\p;
3500:There was no end to my screams.\n;I pleaded.\p;
3600:<i>I</i> <i>d</i><i>o</i><i>n</i><i>'</i><i>t</i> <i>w</i><i>a</i><i>n</i><i>t</i> <i>t</i><i>o</i> <i>d</i><i>i</i><i>e</i><i>!</i>\p;
3700:But nobody heard me.\n;Nobody grabbed my hand.\p;
3800:I simply fell, with the earth coming closer and closer—\p;
3900:〔Mia〕“NOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO!”\p;
4000:〔Mia〕“Aah... hahh... hh... Huh...?”\p;
4100:I had felt my body shatter into a million pieces.\n;But that feeling had disappeared soon after.\p;
4200:When I came to, I found myself collapsed on the roof of Cornelius Tower.\p;
4300:Nishijou-kun was in front of me.\n;He still wasn't looking at me,\n;but he was reaching his hand out even so.\p;
4400:〔Mia〕“Wh...y...”\p;
4500:I had definitely jumped. No doubt about it.\n;I had definitely taken that nearly 180 meter dive and smashed right into the ground.\p;
4600:But now, I just sat there, staring at Nishijou-kun's hand, utterly dumbfounded. I even forgot to wipe away the tears streaming down my face.\p;
4700:〔Takumi〕“Y-You... d-done...?”\p;
4800:Nishijou-kun's words were blunt and curt.\p;
4900:〔Takumi〕“I-I-I'd be in deep shit if you d-died on me...”\p;
5000:〔Takumi〕“It'd look like... I p-pushed you off. I-I-I don't want people to think I-I'm a criminal...”\p;
5100:〔Mia〕“I... was falling... I jumped off... How am I...?”\p;
5200:〔Takumi〕“W-Wasn't that j-just a d-delusion?”\p;
5300:A delusion...?\n;You're telling me all those sensations—all that pain—was just a delusion?\n;That's impossible... It felt so real...\p;
5400:〔Mia〕“Hey, Nishijou-kun...?”\p;
5500:〔Mia〕“Yua-chan... must've felt that same pain when she died...”\p;
5600:〔Mia〕“But I...”\p;
5700:〔Mia〕“I thought I was ready to go through the exact same pain as she did... but I...!”\p;
5800:〔Mia〕“I just kept thinking how much I didn't want to die...!”\p;
5900:〔Mia〕“I was the one who was supposed to die... but as I was falling, I didn't want to...!”\p;
6000:〔Mia〕“I can't jump again... I can't...”\p;
6100:〔Mia〕“After feeling that pain firsthand... I'm too scared... I can't... jump again...”\p;
6200:〔Mia〕“I... What do I do now...?”\p;
6300:〔Takumi〕“Y-You already died once, j-just now.”\p;
6400:〔Mia〕“Huh...?”\p;
6500:〔Takumi〕“Y-You already got to know wh-what Yua felt... I-Isn't that enough...?”\p;
6600:〔Takumi〕“I-I think it's fine to s-start over again, a-and live your life as Kusunoki Mia f-from now on...”\p;
6700:〔Takumi〕“Y-You can... live to the f-fullest, f-for Yua's sake...”\p;
6800:〔Mia〕“Aah... Nnn...!”\p;
6900:〔Mia〕“Th... Thank you... *sniffle*...”\p;
7000:〔Mia〕“Thank.. you... *sob*”\p;
7100:I reached for the hand that he'd extended out to me... and took it.\p;
7200:It was so very...\p;
7300:...very warm.\p;
7400:I could feel his body heat through his palm.\p;
7500:A warmth so comforting, I felt my hands stop shaking.\p;
